Copyright (c) Santander AI Lab

This repository is a collection of stressed datasets. Each dataset is licensed
under the SAME license as its mother (source) dataset, declared in that
dataset's own LICENSE file under datasets/<dataset_name>/LICENSE.

Default collection license: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
(CC BY 4.0) — https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

When a dataset's source carries a different license, that dataset's local
LICENSE file takes precedence for the files within its folder. Always check
the per-dataset LICENSE and attribute both the original source and
Santander AI Lab.
